954
01:17:57,447 --> 01:17:58,800
My Lord

955
01:17:58,887 --> 01:18:00,718
Though I sometimes disagree with you

956
01:18:00,847 --> 01:18:03,680
I have never said a word against you

957
01:18:04,887 --> 01:18:09,085
But this is a choice between right and wrong

958
01:18:09,167 --> 01:18:10,486
I acted for the good of us all

959
01:18:11,247 --> 01:18:13,761
yet you lecture me for being unrighteous

960
01:18:14,167 --> 01:18:17,079
You have followed me so long and for what?

961
01:18:17,127 --> 01:18:19,038
I just want to ensure we live on

962
01:18:42,087 --> 01:18:45,523
There are some things I value more than my life

963
01:19:46,607 --> 01:19:51,078
zhou Yu, may your plans come to fruition

964
01:19:52,007 --> 01:19:53,884
We will fight the good fight

965
01:20:16,007 --> 01:20:17,156
zhou Yu's wife is here

966
01:20:17,647 --> 01:20:18,045
She came alone

967
01:22:12,367 --> 01:22:13,766
zhou Yu

968
01:22:13,927 --> 01:22:16,077
we must alter our plan of attack

969
01:22:17,327 --> 01:22:19,124
Consider your wife's safety

970
01:22:19,247 --> 01:22:20,885
I will send our best men

971
01:22:20,967 --> 01:22:22,958
around back to rescue her

972
01:22:23,807 --> 01:22:25,160
No changes

973
01:22:26,007 --> 01:22:29,283
All our forces must be focused on frontal assault

974
01:22:29,447 --> 01:22:31,244
We cannot divide our strength

975
