Your Honor, we stand alone on the battlefield

976
01:22:35,887 --> 01:22:37,445
Without allied support

977
01:22:37,527 --> 01:22:40,246
the chance for victory seems slight

978
01:22:41,167 --> 01:22:43,283
I have never given up on my dream

979
01:22:43,367 --> 01:22:45,483
Victory cannot rest on dreams alone

980
01:22:51,967 --> 01:22:52,763
When will the east wind come?

981
01:22:53,687 --> 01:22:55,484
If at that time you still trust your friends

982
01:22:56,007 --> 01:22:57,235
light a lantern for a signal

983
01:22:58,087 --> 01:22:59,440
If misfortune befalls Xiao Qiao

984
01:23:00,167 --> 01:23:02,476
will you still fight a war of honor?

985
01:23:08,487 --> 01:23:10,239
I saw you once in the back of your family's estate

986
01:23:11,367 --> 01:23:15,519
Though young, you were already a great beauty

987
01:23:16,007 --> 01:23:17,201
You were studying the tea ceremony

988
01:23:17,287 --> 01:23:19,517
and liked catching butterflies

989
01:23:38,247 --> 01:23:40,681
Did you launch this war for me?

990
01:23:41,007 --> 01:23:42,406
You believe that?

991
01:23:43,607 --> 01:23:46,679
My father was very fond of you

992
01:23:46,927 --> 01:23:49,919
At that time, Cao Cao believed in justice, ideals

993
01:23:49,967 --> 01:23:51,764
and loyalty to the Han throne

994
01:23:52,007 --> 01:23:53,645
He was a young hero

995
01:23:55,247 --> 01:23:59,081
How else could he have become Prime Minister?

996
01:24:00,487 --> 01:24:03,763
By killing many people

997
01:24:08,287 --> 01:24:11,040
I hear many Southland soldiers have fallen ill

998
01:24:11,847 --> 01:24:12,836
Yes

999
01:24:13,847 --> 01:24:15,599
I hear Liu Bei has fled

1000
01:24:16,167 --> 01:24:18,158
and the alliance is broken

1001
01:24:18,887 --> 01:24:20,081
Yes

1002
01:24:20,927 --> 01:24:24,317
Then zhou Yu must be a lonely man

1003
01:24:32,007 --> 01:24:33,360
Did he send you?

1004
01:24:33,527 --> 01:24:34,960
This was my idea

1005
01:24:38,327 --> 01:24:39,476
Why are you here?

1006
01:24:40,567 --> 01:24:42,876
Please withdraw your troops

1007
01:24:43,967 --> 01:24:45,607
Victory is yours

1008
01:24:45,607 --> 01:24:45,687
Victory is yours
What need is there to fight on?

1009
01:24:45,687 --> 01:24:47,006
What need is there to fight on?

1010
01:24:47,607 --> 01:24:48,926
No

1011
01:24:49,727 --> 01:24:53,163
zhou Yu shall kneel before me in surrender

1012
01:24:57,607 --> 01:24:58,801
What is this?

1013
01:25:01,847 --> 01:25:03,883
I am not here for my husband

1014
01:25:04,007 --> 01:25:05,918
but for the people of this kingdom

1015
01:25:06,207 --> 01:25:09,597
Please end this war

1016
01:25:10,767 --> 01:25:13,281
And if I refuse?

1017
01:25:20,487 --> 01:25:21,920
Stop playing

1018
01:25:28,527 --> 01:25:31,803
You must witness how I defeat zhou Yu

1019
01:26:13,287 --> 01:26:14,481
What's on your mind?

1020
01:26:18,487 --> 01:26:20,762
Just thinking of a silly friend

1021
01:26:36,087 --> 01:26:38,806
The times make the hero

1022
01:27:09,167 --> 01:27:10,839
After this battle

1023
01:27:11,487 --> 01:27:13,045
I will have time to savor your tea

1024
01:27:13,287 --> 01:27:15,005
Just one cup?

1025
01:27:15,687 --> 01:27:17,837
Lt'll help you relax

1026
01:27:22,047 --> 01:27:23,241
Fine

1027
01:27:28,167 --> 01:27:30,840
No one's ever given us respect

1028
01:27:31,367 --> 01:27:32,767
So what?

1029
01:27:32,767 --> 01:27:32,807
So what?
Who cares so long as we respect ourselves?

1030
01:27:32,807 --> 01:27:34,718
Who cares so long as we respect ourselves?

1031
01:27:34,927 --> 01:27:35,916
Listen up!

1032
01:27:36,527 --> 01:27:41,078
Our boats will soon charge Cao Cao's fleet

1033
01:27:41,527 --> 01:27:44,963
No man jumps ship until their ships burn

1034
01:27:45,167 --> 01:27:45,917
Yes sir!

1035
01:27:47,007 --> 01:27:48,122
Any problem with that?

1036
01:27:48,287 --> 01:27:49,720
No sir!

1037
01:27:49,807 --> 01:27:50,796
That's what I thought

1038
01:27:51,447 --> 01:27:54,325
Have you all written to your families?

1039
01:27:54,407 --> 01:27:55,840
Yes

1040
01:28:29,167 --> 01:28:30,316
Don't rush

1041
01:28:30,407 --> 01:28:32,716
Appreciate the tea's color and bouquet

1042
01:28:33,207 --> 01:28:34,401
oh

1043
01:28:57,247 --> 01:28:58,680
Why is the Prime Minister waiting to attack?

1044
01:28:58,807 --> 01:29:00,081
The wind is behaving strangely

1045
01:29:00,127 --> 01:29:01,321
I know

1046
01:29:02,007 --> 01:29:03,804
He is drinking tea with that woman

1047
01:29:03,927 --> 01:29:04,882
Tea?

1048
01:29:06,967 --> 01:29:09,561
What makes brewing tea so difficult?

1049
01:29:09,687 --> 01:29:14,124
Leaves, heat, water, and utensils

1050
01:29:14,687 --> 01:29:15,756
all demand study

1051
01:29:21,087 --> 01:29:23,043
Yet the hardest is boiling water

1052
01:29:24,127 --> 01:29:25,162
Boiling water?

1053
01:29:27,087 --> 01:29:28,759
Look!

1054
01:29:30,247 --> 01:29:31,521
The wind has stopped

1055
01:29:41,127 --> 01:29:44,915
At first boil, bubbles hiss and resemble tiny fish eyes

1056
01:29:45,687 --> 01:29:48,599
At second boil, the edge simmers like a fountain

1057
01:29:49,447 --> 01:29:51,756
This is when tea is finest

1058
01:29:52,247 --> 01:29:54,602
At third boil, the water seethes and spurts

1059
01:29:54,847 --> 01:29:58,806
Any further and the water is past its prime

1060
01:30:00,367 --> 01:30:02,835
Your Honor, the wind seems about to shift

1061
01:30:03,087 --> 01:30:05,282
It's time to attack. What are we waiting for?

1062
01:30:05,687 --> 01:30:07,086
Our allies

1063
01:30:07,207 --> 01:30:08,356
What allies?

1064
01:30:13,487 --> 01:30:15,205
Liu Bei fled days ago

1065
01:30:15,247 --> 01:30:17,522
This is all part of zhou Yu's plan

1066
01:30:17,607 --> 01:30:20,167
Some plans are best kept quiet

1067
01:30:24,487 --> 01:30:26,000
Enough! It is full!

1068
01:30:26,367 --> 01:30:27,800
Your Highness

1069
01:30:27,967 --> 01:30:31,164
Don't you see your true self reflected in this tea?

1070
01:30:31,767 --> 01:30:34,156
Your heart is overflowing with ambition

1071
01:30:34,247 --> 01:30:39,037
It's too full to let other people in

1072
01:30:39,807 --> 01:30:42,560
You've carried this full heart to Red Cliff

1073
01:30:43,047 --> 01:30:46,437
Someone here shall pour that heart onto the floor

1074
