1077
01:31:19,367 --> 01:31:20,561
At two o'clock

1078
01:31:20,687 --> 01:31:23,360
the ten fire ships will ram Cao Cao's fleet

1079
01:31:23,447 --> 01:31:24,926
burning through their vanguard

1080
01:31:27,567 --> 01:31:28,556
With the fleet broken

1081
01:31:28,647 --> 01:31:31,241
zhao Yun will hit the east gate

1082
01:31:31,527 --> 01:31:32,960
to divert their attention

1083
01:31:35,927 --> 01:31:38,122
Liu Bei, Guan Yu, and zhang Fei

1084
01:31:38,687 --> 01:31:41,440
will overwhelm Cao Cao's camp from the west gate

1085
01:31:53,727 --> 01:31:55,524
Doctor!

1086
01:31:57,087 --> 01:31:58,315
Your Highness

1087
01:31:58,447 --> 01:32:00,199
Call Doctor Hua Tuo. My head aches

1088
01:32:00,327 --> 01:32:03,558
Your Highness, Hua Tuo has left

1089
01:32:04,287 --> 01:32:06,005
What did you say?

1090
01:32:06,087 --> 01:32:07,315
Hua Tuo is gone

1091
01:33:10,927 --> 01:33:12,679
Cast off!

1092
01:33:23,447 --> 01:33:24,277
What is this wind?

1093
01:33:24,367 --> 01:33:25,846
It's an easterly wind, Your Highness

1094
01:33:26,047 --> 01:33:28,163
It shifted? Lmpossible!

1095
01:33:33,647 --> 01:33:35,285
Enemy ships approaching!

1096
01:33:36,327 --> 01:33:37,999
General, enemy ships approaching!

1097
01:33:38,167 --> 01:33:39,441
Hurry, separate the ships!

1098
01:33:39,527 --> 01:33:40,482
Separate ships!

1099
01:33:52,087 --> 01:33:52,727
