I have done all I can

1105
01:34:09,487 --> 01:34:11,523
Tonight will decide the fate of the empire

1106
01:34:17,047 --> 01:34:18,605
There must be no mistakes

1107
01:34:18,767 --> 01:34:20,325
Zhu-ge Liang

1108
01:34:20,607 --> 01:34:22,325
you weren't lying after all!

1109
01:34:30,007 --> 01:34:30,757
Report!

1110
01:34:30,847 --> 01:34:32,121
Boats are approaching fast

1111
01:34:32,327 --> 01:34:32,998
Separate ships immediately

1112
