1113
01:34:47,447 --> 01:34:48,926
Light the fires!

1114
01:34:56,247 --> 01:34:58,283
Forward

1115
01:35:07,007 --> 01:35:08,440
Hurry over here!

1116
01:35:33,607 --> 01:35:34,756
All speed ahead!

1117
01:36:19,767 --> 01:36:21,723
Hurry, separate the ships

1118
01:36:23,247 --> 01:36:24,839
Faster

1119
01:37:21,607 --> 01:37:23,996
Retreat! Protect the main gate!

1120
01:37:24,887 --> 01:37:29,802
Faster, toward Cao Cao's flagship!

1121
01:39:13,767 --> 01:39:14,961
Strike as powerful as thunder

1122
01:39:50,007 --> 01:39:51,759
Charge!

1123
01:39:52,807 --> 01:39:53,717
Go ahead

1124
01:39:53,847 --> 01:39:54,962
Charge!

1125
01:40:15,767 --> 01:40:16,756
Follow me

1126
01:40:38,527 --> 01:40:39,846
Shoot!

1127
01:40:53,167 --> 01:40:54,122
Launch catapults!

1128
01:41:09,727 --> 01:41:11,365
Hurry, the enemy is approaching

1129
01:41:11,847 --> 01:41:13,166
Look, over there

1130
01:41:34,247 --> 01:41:35,726
Your Highness! Terrible news!

1131
01:41:36,127 --> 01:41:37,480
They have broken through the stockade!

1132
01:41:37,767 --> 01:41:38,961
Why are you panicking?

1133
01:41:40,527 --> 01:41:41,926
Do not forget you are a general

